  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/78624598/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u78624598-13.jpg" class="pil" alt="烟景阳春" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/78624598/">烟景阳春</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          今天上午          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">这本书的作者是个天才。ps看完更感觉到Hamilton音乐剧的伟大，这么厚的一本书居然能浓缩成短短的两个小时却丝毫不损这位美国国父的风采。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
